descriptionHtml:
Best Astrology App of 2019

Astro Guide is very useful guide book for Tarot, Numerology, Horoscope and Palm Reading. Tarot is a mystical and powerful art that has been practiced for thousands of years to tell fortunes, provide psychic readings, and to peer into the past, present, and future tarot reading. If you’ve ever been interested in learning more about the tarot, numerology, palm reading and Horoscope, then you’ve come to the right place.

Astro Guide will reveal the following readings:-
★ Tarot Cards Interpretation
★ Work Tarot Reading
★ Health Tarot Reading
★ Yes No Tarot
★ Romance Tarot Reading
★ Past, Present Future Reading
★ Upright Reverse Tarot Reading
★ Horoscope
★ Daily Horoscope
★ Palm Reading
★ Numerology
★ Palmistry
★ Zodiac Signs

Rider Waite Tarot Interpretation:-

This tarot app will be your guide. There is no ‘right' or ‘wrong' meanings of the Tarot cards. There are traditional interpretations of what the Tarot cards mean, but we encourage you to trust your intuition and go with the meanings that feel right for you. Tarot is all about your intuition. It’s the inner voice of your higher self, and Tarot cards can help you hear your inner voice and embrace its message. This app will also give the description of Health Tarot Reading, Money Tarot Reading, Love Tarot Reading and Yes No Tarot.


Horoscope

Astro Guide is one of the best 2019 horoscope apps on Google play store. Horoscope is the one of the top most forecast tool of astrology. Today Horoscope becomes the most popular in the all age group. This app is developed by keeping all the aspects and interest of all these age groups in mind. In the recent couple of years Horoscope apps become the favorite fortune telling mechanism in peoples. There are twelve zodiac signs in astrology by date of birth.

This app offers to you the deep insight into all the terms of horoscope. We provide the all zodiac signs description.

♈ - Aries
♉ - Taurus
♊ - Gemini
♋ - Cancer
♌ - Leo
♍ - Virgo
♎ - Libra
♏ - Scorpio
♐ - Sagittarius
♑ - Capricorn
♒ - Aquarius
♓ - Pisces

Numerology

Numerology is a part of three major pillars of predictive science. There are astrology, palmistry and numerology. Numerology uses numbers as a key to human behaviors. There are nine planets which have greater influence on the human life and each of them has been allotted a particular number. The moment a person is born, he is governed by a certain principal planet and the secondary planet is governed by the numbers allotted to these planets. Numerology Reading can provide his physiology, thinking, reason, emotions, ambitions, likes, dislikes, health, career etc.

Different Different Astrologers choose the different different ways to predict with numbers they may choose Name Numerology, Birthdate numerology or may take the both, depends upon their way to calculate. The Numerology App is developed to keeping all the above things in mind. This Numerology App will take your Numerology name and Numerology Birthdate as the basic details to create your numerology report. This Numerology Report will be able to predict your past present and future predictions. This App use Name Numerology Calculator in background to calculate the Numerology Number. You can use the same calculator in the app menu to calculate anyone’s name numerology number.

Palmistry

Palm Reading app offers you a free palm reading. Based on your palm lines you can find all about your future. Hand Reading or palmistry is most favorable way to predict future. This app interprets person’s characters; predict their personality and much more by analyzing user hand. Our Palm Reading app make this process easy and automatic. Let this astrology app to scan your palm reading lines and let analyze your hand lines. Get benefit from our palm reader app, the most accurate and perfect fortune telling utility tool. This palm reading app explain the all major lines of palm like line of life, line of fate, line of heart, line of head and much more.
